<div class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-inner">
      <div style="margin-bottom:24px"><img src="{{ 'logo.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Thakar Kitchen" style="height:90px;width:auto;max-width:200px;object-fit:contain;background:#fff;border-radius:4px;padding:5px 14px;"/></div>
      <h1>Our <em>Story</em> —<br/>From Kitchen to Your Heart</h1>
      <p>Thakar Kitchen was born out of a deep love for authentic Indian flavors and a desire to bring the warmth of homemade food to every household across India.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
<div class="about-story">
    <div class="about-story-text">
      <h2>Rooted in <em>Tradition</em>,<br/>Built for Today</h2>
      <p>Founded in 1967 by Karunashankar Thakar in Morbi, Gujarat, Group of Thakar has been Gujarat's trusted name in sattvic vegetarian cuisine and hospitality for over five decades. What began as a small family venture with one mission — to preserve the authentic taste of Indian home cooking — has grown into a celebrated multi-brand legacy, guided by the same founding values of purity, tradition, and wholesome cooking.</p>
      <p>Every recipe we use has been passed down through generations, tested in real kitchens, perfected over decades, and cooked with the same care as if it were made for family. That philosophy lives on in every product we create today.</p>
      <p>We honor that heritage while embracing innovation. Our preservative-free, ready-to-eat delicacies bring the richness of traditional Gujarat and North Indian recipes straight to your doorstep — crafted with quality ingredients, sealed with advanced packaging, and delivered fresh all year round.</p>
      <p>Today, we proudly serve over 10,000 happy customers across India — and we're just getting started.</p>
      <p><em>Five decades of tradition. A future built on flavor.</em></p>
    </div>
    <!-- TODO: move this image to Shopify files -->
    <div class="about-img"><img src="https://thakarkitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/WhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-12.14.33-PM-231x231.jpeg" alt="Our Kitchen"/></div>
  </div>
<div class="about-values">
    <h2 style="font-family:Cormorant Garamond,serif">What We <em style="color:var(--gold);font-style:italic">Stand For</em></h2>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card"><div class="value-icon"><svg width="36" height="36" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;color:var(--gold)"><use href="#ico-leaf"/></svg></div><div class="value-title">Pure & Natural</div><div class="value-desc">No artificial colors, preservatives, or flavors. Just real ingredients, real taste.</div></div>
      <div class="value-card"><div class="value-icon"><svg width="36" height="36" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;color:var(--gold)"><use href="#ico-users"/></svg></div><div class="value-title">Family First</div><div class="value-desc">Every product is made with the same care we would give our own family meals.</div></div>
      <div class="value-card"><div class="value-icon"><svg width="36" height="36" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;color:var(--gold)"><use href="#ico-award"/></svg></div><div class="value-title">Quality Always</div><div class="value-desc">We never compromise on quality — from sourcing to cooking to packaging.</div></div>
      <div class="value-card"><div class="value-icon"><svg width="36" height="36" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;color:var(--gold)"><use href="#ico-handshake"/></svg></div><div class="value-title">Farmer Support</div><div class="value-desc">We partner directly with local farmers to ensure freshness and support communities.</div></div>
      <div class="value-card"><div class="value-icon"><svg width="36" height="36" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;color:var(--gold)"><use href="#ico-recycle"/></svg></div><div class="value-title">Sustainable</div><div class="value-desc">Eco-friendly packaging and responsible sourcing for a better tomorrow.</div></div>
      <div class="value-card"><div class="value-icon"><svg width="36" height="36" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;color:var(--gold)"><use href="#ico-heart"/></svg></div><div class="value-title">Made with Love</div><div class="value-desc">Every meal is crafted with genuine passion for good food and good living.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

